      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个状态图，展示从开发到最终应用部署的完整流程。起点应该是开发者，终点是应用上线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Developer",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，起点是开发者。那开发者之后直接到应用吗？还是中间有一些基础设施的环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Application",
        "Infrastructure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间有好几步。开发者要对接基础设施团队，同时也要处理配置，所以开发者应该分出两条线：一条到基础设施，一条到configMap配置。然后基础设施和configMap之间也要有交互。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把开发者到基础设施、开发者到configMap，以及基础设施和configMap之间的双向关系加上。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "configMap之后流向哪里？是直接进入Kubernetes，还是有其他中间节点？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "configMap",
        "Kubernetes"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "configMap直接到Kubernetes，Kubernetes部署完成后产生Application，最后Application到终点。这样整个链路就闭环了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "configMap",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application",
        "[*]"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下整体结构：起点[*]→Developer，Developer分别连接Infrastructure和configMap，Infrastructure和configMap互相连接，configMap→Kubernetes→Application→终点[*]。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Developer",
        "Infrastructure",
        "configMap",
        "Kubernetes",
        "Application"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，就是这个流程。开发者启动，经过基础设施和配置管理，最终通过Kubernetes部署应用上线。",
      "elements_involved": [
